Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Typhoon Passes - Illusion and Reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your dad was a tanker?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was one of the\Nlegendary heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who led over a thousand\Ncitizens and soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,out of the surrounded\Ncity of Wardenburk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in just six Type-2 Millipads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he was wounded\Nin battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he met my mother, who was a medic\Nat the hospital he went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you ended up their kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! What a wonderful potato...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took such good care\Nof them, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to share some\Nwith the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Claus-san is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll give him\Nsome as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It isn't that I like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know she could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's started to blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's going to get bad soon.\NWe should go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't something strange\Nabout Rio-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way she was playing\Nthat trumpet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems kind of down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai never talks\Nmore than she has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I know! Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tempura was\Ngood, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! The potatoes\Nwere so crisp...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Rio.\NEat up while it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was scarfing down\Nthe green peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai, eating peppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how chopped-up\Nthey are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai always finds the peppers\Nand takes them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Claus-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Desert Wolf, Miracle Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On his left breast, a wolf's head\Ntattoo symbolizes the glory
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and unity of the 481st platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry too much, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing with the captain was\Noverthinking on our parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause it's Rio-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cool, awesome,\Nand so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she conquered her hatred of green\Npeppers and can eat them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan, you really\Nlike her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the person I look up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too, but...\NWhat do you think, Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. She can have\Nhalf my bed, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, you grab that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot to turn off\Nthe fire in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you seem so on top of things, but actually\Naren't, is one of your charm points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, there's been\Ntoo much of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret hanging\Nup on your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover for your problems\Nwith your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least be an awesome sempai\Nwhen they're around, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for dropping by so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Class-1 Priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant Rio Kazumiya\Nof the 1121 Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Desert Wolf couldn't\Ngo anywhere in this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an apology, how about\Nsome hot tea and a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for completing your\Nmission in this typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry all we have is\Nleftovers from dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've woken me\Nup when he got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even good cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The green peppers\Nare quality, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who picked\Nand fried them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be quite a wife someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a new paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Major brought\Nit with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the peace talks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The conference isn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither side's conditions\Nare being met...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Princess Iliya were still alive,\Nthings might be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Iliya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know her?\NShe was the hero of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first princess of\NArchduke Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Helvetian army's\Ngoddess of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a tanker goddess, right up there\Nwith Claus the Desert Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, that's actually-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Yumina's kids has\Nbeen missing all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san, who vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The river's risen quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fields downstream haven't\Nbeen harvested yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dam breaks, they're all done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me around, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only took my eyes off\Nhim for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search and rescue\Nis an army's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. There's so much water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came out here because you\Nhave some idea where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Seiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan loves eggplants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone used their\Nallowances and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya must've...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, downriver\Nin the middle of a typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must protect the eggplants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's risking their\Nlives for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being such a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids without parents have to be stronger\Nthan those who have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you cause trouble for people,\Nyou're not the only one they get angry at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get mad at Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your big sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an orphan, too. So I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to keep whining?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you've worked really\Nhard to raise something,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you value it the same\Nas your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are big enough\Nto be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be great pickled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun's started going back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, they have no way\Nto get back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with Miracle Claus now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground's starting to collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flooding's making the\Nground crumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This is why I hate kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids who don't listen should just be tied\Nup and locked in a room somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will scaring them do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know they're always\Nwatching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... That was too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm sure it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claus-san is supposed to\Nbe a miracle worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the Desert Wolf\Nor Miracle Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just happens to have the same name\Nand close to the same appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they first met, Kureha just decided\Nit on her own and got all happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how he doesn't\Nreally talk much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just never found the\Nright time to tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to think of how\Nto save those two down there:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the courier with years of\Nservice but nothing else,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the one with tons of enthusiasm,\Nbut no experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them a rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no good spot above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's too far to send\Nit from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a way to get\Nthem the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my dad would have been\Nlike you if he were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell everyone that I knew\Nmy dad really well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's all second-hand information.\NI don't actually know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died when I was very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the upper left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linear Anchoring Coil online.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting System partially\Nonline from B7 to F5.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Initiating targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire the wire anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, in your late father's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull up the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe now, so I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the person I admire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blue sky after a typhoon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you kept it up the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw her eyes,\Nher total faith in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was more scared of breaking\Nher dreams than of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I guess I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wonderful, Claus-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the time, what you\Nthink you see in a person
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what they're really\Nfeeling are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiring someone always\Nmakes your vision blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, when you're looked at\Nin that way, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you can't stay\Nuntil she wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this is the most honorable\Nwound I've ever received!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A Departure - The First Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The First Snow.
